reer  personal life  references  external links early lifeedit roosevelt was born on november   to congressman james roosevelt – and romelle theresa schneider – his two full siblings are michael born december   and anna born january   through his father he has two elder halfsisters sara and kate a younger halfbrother hall and a younger halfsister rebecca his paternal grandparents were president franklin delano roosevelt – and first lady eleanor roosevelt – roosevelt graduated from la salle high school in pasadena in  he earned his ab with honors in government from harvard college in  he later received his jd from harvard law school and completed the advanced management program at harvard business school careeredit on june   following his graduation from harvard he was commissioned in the naval reserve and rose to the rank of lieutenant on july   after obtaining his jd from harvard law roosevelt spent  years as partner at choate hall  stewart in boston massachusetts roosevelt was the associate commissioner for retirement policy for the social security administration before joining tufts health plan in  as senior vice president and general counsel he held that position until june  when he became president and chief executive officer of tufts health plan in  he ran for congress losing the democratic primary to joseph p kennedy ii he has also served as chief legal counsel for the massachusetts democratic party he is past chairman of the board of trustees for the massachusetts hospital association past president of the american health lawyers association and past chairman of the board of trustees for mount auburn hospital currently roosevelt serves as chairman of the board of directors for massachusetts association of health plans and as a member of the boards at americas health insurance plans catholic democrats emmanuel college and the kenneth b schwartz center he was called upon in  to oversee hearings on controversies related to seating delegates from florida and michigan to the  democratic national convention roosevelt was described as detailoriented and as having great institutional knowledge he had not publicly endorsed either clinton or obama before the committee meeting personal lifeedit on june   roosevelt married ann martha conlon born march   the daughter of walter n conlon and a  graduate of radcliffe college together they have three daughters kathleen ann roosevelt born  who married jeffrey walker in  theresa marie tracy roosevelt born  who married robert o’loughlin in  maura amy roosevelt born  who married joshua fisher in  referencesedit  httpwwwfdrlibrarymaristeduarchivesresourcesgenealogyhtml  social security death index retrieved    register of officers of the naval reserve   tufts health plan senior management group retrieved    httpwwwourcampaignscomracedetailhtmlraceid  npr whos who on the rules and bylaws committee  mydd vote counting the dnc rules  bylaws committee  cnncom its decision day for democrats archived  at the wayback machine  bachrach bradford  november  ann conlon is betrothed to james roosevelt jr the new york times retrieved  april    times special to the new york  june  james roosevelt it weds ann conlon st pauls church in cambridge is the scene oi bridal the new york times retrieved  april    httpwwwfdrlibrarymaristeduarchivesresourcesgenealogyhtml  kathleen roosevelt jeffrey walker the new york times  august  retrieved  april    tracy roosevelt robert o’loughlin the new york times  august  retrieved  april    maura roosevelt and joshua fisher the new york times  july  retrieved  april   external linksedit appearances on cspan v t e franklin d roosevelt nd president of the united states – th governor of new york – assistant secretary of the navy – new york state senator – presidency inaugurations st nd rd th new deal overview new deal coalition first  days second new deal federal emergency relief administration civilian conservation corps agricultural adjustment administration emergency banki