ty calif james roosevelt sr     genealogy please wait loading people projects discussions surnames log in email password log in dont know your password log in with facebook join  its free home people projects genealogy dna tests geni requires javascript please enable javascript in your browsers settings to use this part of geni join the worlds largest family tree gender male female first name last name email never shared never spammed start my family tree or cancel james roosevelt sr ‹ back to roosevelt surname is your surname roosevelt research the roosevelt family start your family tree now james roosevelt srs geni profile contact profile manager view family tree share your family tree and photos with the people you know and love build your family tree online share photos and videos smart matching™ technology free get started share tweet this related projects notable businesspeople union college james roosevelt sr birthdate july    birthplace hyde park dutchess new york united states death december    hyde park dutchess new york united states place of burial hyde park dutchess new york united states immediate family son of dr isaac daniel roosevelt and mary rebecca roosevelt husband of rebecca brien roosevelt and sara ann sallie roosevelt father of james rosy roosevelt jr and franklin d roosevelt nd president of the usa brother of john aspinwall roosevelt occupation lawyer ice business farmer managed by john patrick mccaffrey last updated june   view complete profile historical records matching james roosevelt sr james roosevelt in wikitree james roosevelt collection wikitree birth july    hyde park new york death dec    new york wife sara delano view the record james roosevelt in wikitree james roosevelt collection wikitree birth july    hyde park dutchess new york death dec    hyde park dutchess new york parents isaac roosevelt mary rebecca aspinwall wife rebecca brien howland sara delano view the record james roosevelt in wikitree james roosevelt collection wik